{"tid":821426,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【山竹襲港】大角嘴唐樓吹到散   頂層外牆成幅倒冧","createTime":"2018-09-16T02:56:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T03:06:20.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"91060716e31d3fa39efd559aa87d27ae2f9a08de","tid":821426,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T02:56:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180916/large/1537065801_30d3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180916%2Flarge%2F1537065801_30d3.jpg&h=e36f9ebf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180916/large/1537065801_5456.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180916%2Flarge%2F1537065801_5456.jpg&h=2ff8afd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n強颱風「山竹」吹襲下，大角嘴道與福利街交界一幢唐樓，在狂風暴雨下，頂層外牆整幅倒冧，並飛墮到街上。住港灣豪庭的游小姐，早上10時許，在家中望出對面大角嘴道與福利街一幢唐樓，赫見驚人一幕，「出面大風大雨，開始見到唐樓6樓天台部份外牆郁郁吓，然後裂痕越來越大，外牆有棵約1.6米高的大樹纏住生長，結果最尾大樹連根拔起，同整幅石屎一起飛墮街上。」<br />\n<br />\n游小姐嚇得目瞪口呆，她猶有餘悸表示，地下有間地皮屋，「好危險，有啲掃街阿姐會係果度掃街，如果當時係度就好危險，好驚，好危險！」她指唐樓天台有數隻天線「接收器」，已被吹至打橫卧地，她擔心會飛落街，她已報警求助。"},{"pid":"d45529162415145524835af57f06fb259d08c0c7","tid":821426,"uid":27630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91060716e31d3fa39efd559aa87d27ae2f9a08de","tid":821426,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T02:56:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180916/large/1537065801_30d3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180916%2Flarge%2F1537065801_30d3.jpg&h=e36f9ebf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180916/large/1537065801_5456.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180916%2Flarge%2F1537065801_5456.jpg&h=2